{"tid":2064117,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Super Mario Maker 2 被指「辱華」　中國網店全線下架","createTime":"2020-06-14T14:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T16:33:31.000Z","uid":105567,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"499847acb2b3fbbcf7d6218057548361154b8cad","tid":2064117,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"中國對於網上內容，包括遊戲內的字眼都有嚴格的審查，水貨遊戲則是灰色地帶。最近有 Super Mario Maker 2 玩家在遊戲的自製關卡內加入諷刺字句，被中國網民發現後，網店已經全面下架無法購買。<br />\n<br />\nSuper Mario Maker 2（超級瑪利歐創作家2）是個讓玩家自己創作 Mario 關卡，然後與其他玩家分享交流的遊戲，而當中無論用戶名稱或者關卡命名都是可以自由創作。最近有中國玩家發現遊戲內有「牆國聖上習煬帝首作」和「朱明錦衣衛，大清文字獄，不及振梁家貴族禁評」等有諷刺成分的關卡名稱，連用戶名稱也是「8964」，大逆不道，結果淘寶和京東等大型網上零售平台都全線將這個遊戲下架，玩家無法購買實體遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/14/super-mario-maker-2-glass-heart/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F14%2Fsuper-mario-maker-2-glass-heart%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8ktjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=62546cbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/14/super-mario-maker-2-glass-heart/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"892c9042f8b873409b20fb8aa3b019470848cc0e","tid":2064117,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"支那人唔配自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca0541132922bc6382d6ac768faeda9b4673d9f","tid":2064117,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:45:45.000Z","msg":"笑左"},{"pid":"2c757bbf6f19f038fe22994f9e7316e8b2be5f11","tid":2064117,"uid":160261,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kUsbz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kUsbz.png&h=188d89f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21aaca873195ce90aa8ae0a3ab4368bb7a637e3f","tid":2064117,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T14:49:1